OL,6,FProactive Scottish Borders Council
OL,7,Ftops the charts in Scotland for
OL,8,Fpothole-filling success, according to
OL,9,Fa new study.
OL,11,FThe Borders has emerged as the area
OL,12,Fthat carries out the most pothole
OL,13,Frepairs.
OL,15,FThe local authority is rated the third
OL,16,Fbest in Great Britain and the only
OL,17,Flocal authority in Scotland in the top
OL,18,Ften list - revealed by online car
OL,19,Fretailer Cinch.
