OL,6,FCinch has shared data from Freedom of
OL,7,FInformation requests that were
OL,8,Fsubmitted to all 207 road-maintaining
OL,9,Fauthorities in Great Britain to
OL,10,Funcover the scale of the nation's
OL,11,Fpothole problem.
OL,13,FThe area of Scotland that has carried
OL,14,Fout the most pothole repairs since
OL,15,F2022 was found to be Scottish Borders
OL,16,FCouncil ` with 157,545 repairs.
OL,18,FThis puts it at number three on the
OL,19,Fnationwide list, behind Devon County
OL,20,FCouncil and Surrey County Council.
