OL,6,FMany road users our reporter spoke to
OL,7,Fin Galashiels were surprised by the
OL,8,Ffigures, arguing that several Borders
OL,9,Froads were still in poor condition and
OL,10,Fthat the council need to do more to
OL,11,Fmake them better.
OL,13,FHowever part of the issue is that
OL,14,Froads often deteriorate faster than
OL,15,Fresurfacing works can keep pace with -
OL,16,Fan with 3000km of road in the Borders
OL,17,Fthe council have a large surface area
OL,18,Fto look after.
