OL,6,FScottish Borders Council's roads
OL,7,Fdepartment have credited their
OL,8,Fapparent success to a new piece of
OL,9,Ftechnology - which repairs potholes
OL,10,Fmore efficiently. But they say it's
OL,11,Fstill a significant challenge.
OL,13,F"What we would like to do is more
OL,14,Fresurfacing, because then we would
OL,15,Freduce the number of potholes that we
OL,16,Fwould have to repair" explained John
OL,17,FGreenwell, portfolio holder for Roads
OL,18,FMaintenance and Improvements.
