OL,4,Cpothole repairs
OL,6,F"We have invested significantly in
OL,7,Fmachinery - the Pothole Pro was an
OL,8,Finvestment made by the council to
OL,9,Fimprove how we we fix our potholes.
OL,11,FIt fixes, permanently- as much as we
OL,12,Fcan say permanently - but, it's far
OL,13,Fbetter than what was done previously,
OL,14,Fwhere we just filled a hole, patted it
OL,15,Fdown, and went on to the next one. We
OL,16,Fuse fewer vehicles and man power, and
OL,17,Fthere are health improvements as the
OL,18,Fguys don't need to use pneumatic
OL,19,Fdrills as much.
