OL,6,FFour years ago Scottish Borders
OL,7,FCouncil acquired a JCB Pothole Pro `
OL,8,Fwhich costs around #165,000 or can be
OL,9,Fhired for around #600 a month ` amid
OL,10,Fgrowing concern at the poor state of
OL,11,Fthe region's roads.
OL,13,FITV Border were out with the roads
OL,14,Fteam near Melrose and watched the
OL,15,FPothole Pro in action. It's currently
OL,16,Fout on Borders roads five days a week.
