OL,6,FIt combines three machines in one and
OL,7,Fcan repair a pothole in less than
OL,8,Feight minutes ` four times quicker
OL,9,Fthan standard methods and at half the
OL,10,Fcost of current solutions.
OL,12,FBetween April and June 2025 workers
OL,13,Fcommenced or successfully completed
OL,14,Ften surface dressing patching sites `
OL,15,Fcovering an area of approximately
OL,16,F10,700m2.
